title: [MegaDrive] Sonic the Hedgehog 2 Soundtrack
description:
This Soundtrack has been brought to you by The 16-bit Audiophile Project.

Our goal is to give retrogaming fans the chance of listening to the music of the 16-bit console era with the highest quality possible reproduced by their original hardware (no emulators!) and recorded with top notch quality.

Folder info:

 = Hi resolution FLACs, sampled at 96 Khz and 24 bit
 = Standard resolution FLACs, sampled at CD quality (44.1 Khz and 16 bit)
 = MP3 quality sampled at 192 kbps

Check our website for updates on future releases and more soundtracks!
